{"translation-revision-date":"YEAR-MO-DA HO:MI+ZONE","generator":"WP-CLI\/2.12.0","source":"src\/bplugins-admin\/Components\/Settings.js","domain":"messages","locale_data":{"messages":{"":{"domain":"messages","lang":"en","plural-forms":"nplurals=2; plural=(n != 1);"},"Failed to save setting.":[""],"Are you sure? This will permanently delete all Panorama Viewer data (panoramas, product spots, virtual tours, and all settings) when the plugin is uninstalled.":[""],"Delete Data on Uninstall":[""],"When enabled, all plugin data will be permanently deleted when you uninstall (delete) the plugin. This includes:":[""],"All Panorama posts (bppiv-image-viewer post type)":[""],"All Product Spot posts (product_spot post type)":[""],"All Virtual Tour posts (virtual_tour post type)":[""],"All panorama and hotspot configurations and metadata":[""],"All plugin settings and options":[""],"\u26a0\ufe0f This action cannot be undone. Your data will be safe if you only deactivate the plugin.":[""],"Data will be deleted on uninstall":[""],"Data will be preserved on uninstall":[""]}}}